# Preference Signal Refinery

A scalable starter system for ingesting pairwise preference events, learning user/item vectors, clustering users, and exposing the engine through an API.

## Features

- Pairwise preference ingestion
- Online vector updates
- Event weighting via confidence + dwell time
- SQLite storage
- User clustering
- User profile export
- FastAPI API

## Install

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt

Run API

uvicorn app.main:app --reload

Run tests

pytest -q

Example endpoints
	•	POST /events
	•	GET /users/{user_id}/profile
	•	GET /clusters
	•	POST /train/rebuild

Notes

This is an MVP scaffold.
It is not yet production hardened.
Future upgrades:
	•	Postgres
	•	auth
	•	batch jobs
	•	privacy-preserving aggregation
	•	sequence modeling
	•	cross-domain embeddings

:::

